primary.context: Customer has never logged in before and needs access to the owner portal
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller, updated the contact information for delivery, and confirmed sending the Clubhouse registration link.

steps: Caller requested help logging into their account.
Agent performed account lookup via phone number and verified identity (name and state).
Agent identified the need for a Clubhouse registration link.
Agent confirmed contact details and corrected the email and phone number based on user input.
Agent confirmed the link was being sent and the user expressed satisfaction.

clarifications.note: Agent proactively suggests Clubhouse link for login
Agent re-confirms phone after email correction

corrections.note: User corrects email and one digit of phone

actions.detail: Verified name Roy Norman and state Florida

insights.summary: The customer wanted to access their owner account for the first time. The AI successfully verified the user, updated their email address, and sent a Clubhouse registration link.
